(120, 1, '2014-10-13 11:11:25', '2014-10-13 09:11:25', '<!--:sk--><p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Ponkame </strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Bohat repertor folklrneho sboru Technik poskytuje znan variabilitu v monostiach.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Vieme Vm ponknu <strong>komornej program</strong> vtrvan cca 20 mint, ktor je zaujmav najm pre spoloensk podujatia, akmi s recepcie, narodeninov oslavy, rzne firemn udalosti, plesy, posedenia sVaimi obchodnmi partnermi, iprezentcia Vaej spolonosti partnerom vzahrani.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Vprpade zujmu <strong>oceloveern program</strong> Vm vieme ponknu a 100 mint hodnotne umelecky spracovanch piesn atancov zcelho Slovenska vpodan 46 inkujcich. Vprograme njdete reginy Tekova, itnho ostrova, Novohradu, Podpoania, Horehronia, Trenianskych i Goralskch oblast, i Zemplna.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>\r\nSlovensk udov hudba</strong> navod pri kadej spoloenskej prleitosti vemi</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">prjemn atmosfru. Aj vtomto Vm vieme vyjs vstrety. Naa <strong>kapela a</strong> <strong>dievensk spevcka skupina</strong> Vm so svojm repertorom sprjemn as aponka a niekoko hodn zbavy  ato <strong>bohatm programom</strong> piesn a meldi z celho Slovenska iokolitch krajn.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"></p><!--:--><!--:en--><p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>We offer</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">An abundant repertory of folklore ensemble Technik provides aconsiderable variability in possibilities.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We can offer You a<strong>chamber programme</strong> with duration of approximately 20 minutes, which is interesting especially for social events such as banquets, birthday celebrations, various company events, balls, sittings with Your business partners or presentation of Your company to foreign partners.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">In case of being interested in <strong>afull-length programme</strong>, we can offer You up to 100 minutes of valuably and artistically processed songs and dances from all over Slovakia, presented by 46 performers. You can find regions of Tekov, itn Island, Novohrad, Podpoanie, Horehronie, Zempln, Trenn or Goral in the programme.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="line-height: 1.5;"><strong>Slovak folklore music</strong> induces avery enjoyable atmosphere on any social occasion, therefore we can also meet Your demands in this sphere. <strong>Our band together with our female singing group</strong> will make Your time pleasant with its repertory as it offers up to several hours of entertainment which a<strong>rich programme</strong> of songs and melodies from around Slovakia and surrounding countries.</span><strong><br />\r\n</strong></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<!--:--><!--:de--><p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Ponkame </strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Bohat repertor folklrneho sboru Technik poskytuje znan variabilitu v monostiach.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://localhost/technik/fotovideo/foto/img_2237"><img class="alignleft wp-image-298 size-medium" src="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_2237-300x300.jpg" alt="IMG_2237" width="300" height="300" /></a>Vieme Vm ponknu <strong>komornej program</strong> vtrvan cca 20 mint, ktor je zaujmav najm pre spoloensk podujatia, akmi s recepcie, narodeninov oslavy, rzne firemn udalosti, plesy, posedenia sVaimi obchodnmi partnermi, iprezentcia Vaej spolonosti partnerom vzahrani.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_2417.jpg"><img class=" size-medium wp-image-309 alignright" src="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_2417-300x200.jpg" alt="IMG_2417" width="300" height="200" /></a>Vprpade zujmu <strong>oceloveern program</strong> Vm vieme ponknu a 100 mint hodnotne umelecky spracovanch piesn atancov zcelho Slovenska vpodan 46 inkujcich. Vprograme njdete reginy Tekova, itnho ostrova, Novohradu, Podpoania, Horehronia, Trenianskych i Goralskch oblast, i Zemplna.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><a href="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_2183.jpg"><img class="alignleft wp-image-295 size-thumbnail" src="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_2183-150x150.jpg" alt="IMG_2183" width="150" height="150" /></a></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><img class=" wp-image-288 size-thumbnail alignright" src="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/DSC7148-150x150.jpg" alt="technik_foto" width="150" height="150" />Slovensk udov hudba</strong> navod pri kadej spoloenskej prleitosti vemi</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">prjemn atmosfru. Aj vtomto Vm vieme vyjs vstrety. Naa <strong>kapela a</strong> <strong>dievensk spevcka skupina</strong> Vm so svojm repertorom sprjemn as aponka a niekoko hodn zbavy  ato <strong>bohatm programom</strong> piesn a meldi z celho Slovenska iokolitch krajn.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<p></p>\r\n<!--:-->', '<!--:sk-->Ponkame<!--:--><!--:en-->We offer<!--:--><!--:de-->OCHTEFERIFTUCH<!--:-->', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'program', '', '', '2015-03-14 21:02:05', '2015-03-14 20:02:05', '', 116, 'http://localhost/technik/?page_id=120', 0, 'page', '', 0),
