(397, 1, '2015-01-03 00:04:59', '2015-01-02 23:04:59', '<!--:sk--><p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Ponkame </strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Bohat repertor folklrneho sboru Technik poskytuje znan variabilitu v monostiach.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://localhost/technik/fotovideo/foto/img_2237"><img class="alignleft wp-image-298 size-medium" src="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_2237-300x300.jpg" alt="IMG_2237" width="300" height="300" /></a>Vieme Vm ponknu <strong>komornej program</strong> vtrvan cca 20 mint, ktor je zaujmav najm pre spoloensk podujatia, akmi s recepcie, narodeninov oslavy, rzne firemn udalosti, plesy, posedenia sVaimi obchodnmi partnermi, iprezentcia Vaej spolonosti partnerom vzahrani.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_2417.jpg"><img class=" size-medium wp-image-309 alignright" src="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_2417-300x200.jpg" alt="IMG_2417" width="300" height="200" /></a>Vprpade zujmu <strong>oceloveern program</strong> Vm vieme ponknu a 100 mint hodnotne umelecky spracovanch piesn atancov zcelho Slovenska vpodan 46 inkujcich. Vprograme njdete reginy Tekova, itnho ostrova, Novohradu, Podpoania, Horehronia, Trenianskych i Goralskch oblast, i Zemplna.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><a href="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_2183.jpg"><img class="alignleft wp-image-295 size-thumbnail" src="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_2183-150x150.jpg" alt="IMG_2183" width="150" height="150" /></a></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><img class=" wp-image-288 size-thumbnail alignright" src="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/DSC7148-150x150.jpg" alt="technik_foto" width="150" height="150" />Slovensk udov hudba</strong> navod pri kadej spoloenskej prleitosti vemi</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">