er" src="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_0147-300x200.jpg" alt="IMG_0147" width="300" height="200" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Since its formation, the ensemble took part in more than 2000 performances at various folklore events either at home or abroad. One of the most significant events is undoubtedly participation in an international festival in Orlando, Florida in 2000, where we managed to perform at unbelievable 43 shows in only 14 days.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The ensemble has yet edited and released <strong>3 musical CDs</strong>, namely: In our yard /2003/, as the youngsters dawdled along/2009/ and From album/2012/, under directional and artistic oversight of tefan Molota.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Presently, the ensemble has <strong>68 members</strong>. It consists of <strong>musical section, female singing group and numerous dance section</strong>. Members of the ensemble are students of both high schools and universities of Bratislava, but also working youth, all of which are united in admiration and respect for Slovak folklore  beautiful heritage of our ancestors.</p><!--:--><!--:de--><p>\r\n<p><strong>Ons </strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Folklrny sbor Technik STU sa rad medzi <strong>najstarie folklrne sbory na Slovensku</strong>. Vo svojej tvorbe sa zameriava na scnick spracovvanie slovenskho udovho dedistva, ato v podobe <strong>zvykov, piesn, hudby, tancov ikrojov.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_0147.jpg"><img class=" size-medium wp-image-287 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_0147-300x200.jpg" alt="IMG_0147" width="300" height="200" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Od svojho vzniku absolvoval sbor viac ako 2000 vystpen na rznych folklrnych podujatiach doma i v zahrani. Medzi najvznamnejie sa bez pochyby rad as na medzinrodnom festivale v Orlande na Floride vroku 2000, kde sme poas 14 dn stihli odvystupova neuveritench 43 predstaven.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Sbor doposia spracoval avydal tie <strong>3 hudobn CD nosie</strong>  Vnaom dvore /2003/, inuli sa mldenci /2009/ a Zalbumu /2012/ - pod reijnou a umeleckou taktovkou tefana Molotu.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">V sasnosti m sbor <strong>68 lenov</strong>. Tvor ho <strong>hudobn zloka, dievensk spevcka skupina apoetn tanen zloka</strong>. lenovia sboru s tudenti bratislavskch strednch avysokch kl, ale aj pracujca mlde, ktor spja cta aobdiv kslovenskmu folklru -krsnemu dedistvu naich predkov.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<p></p>\r\n<!--:-->', '<!--:sk-->O ns<!--:--><!--:en-->About us<!--:--><!--:de-->Onaischen<!--:-->', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '116-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-14 20:56:23', '2015-03-14 19:56:23', '', 116, 'http://localhost/technik/archives/618', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(619, 9, '2015-03-14 21:01:18', '2015-03-14 20:01:18', '<!--:sk--><p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Ponkame </strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Bohat repertor folklrneho sboru Technik poskytuje znan variabilitu v monostiach.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Vieme Vm ponknu <strong>komornej program</strong> vtrvan cca 20 mint, ktor je zaujmav najm pre spoloensk podujatia, akmi s recepcie, narodeninov oslavy, rzne firemn udalosti, plesy, posedenia sVaimi obchodnmi partnermi, iprezentcia Vaej spolonosti partnerom vzahrani.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Vprpade zujmu <strong>oceloveern program</strong> Vm vieme ponknu a 100 mint hodnotne umelecky spracovanch piesn atancov zcelho Slovenska vpodan 46 inkujcich. Vprograme njdete reginy Tekova, itnho ostrova, Novohradu, Podpoania, Horehronia, Trenianskych i Goralskch oblast, i Zemplna.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>\nSlovensk udov hudba</strong> navod pri kadej spoloenskej prleitosti vemi</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">prjemn atmosfru. Aj vtomto Vm vieme vyjs vstrety. Naa <strong>kapela a</strong> <strong>dievensk spevcka skupina</strong> Vm so svojm repertorom sprjemn as aponka a niekoko hodn zbavy  ato <strong>bohatm programom</strong> piesn a meldi z celho Slovenska iokolitch krajn.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"></p><!--:--><!--:en--><p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>We offer</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">An abundant repertory of folklore ensemble Technik provides aconsiderable variability in possibilities.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We can offer You a<strong>chamber programme</strong> with duration of approximately 20 minutes, which is interesting especially for social events such as banquets, birthday celebrations, various company events, balls, sittings with Your business partners or presentation of Your company to foreign partners.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">In case of being interested in <strong>afull-length programme</strong>, we can offer You up to 100 minutes of valuably and artistically processed songs and dances from all over Slovakia, presented by 46 performers. You can find regions of Tekov, itn Island, Novohrad, Podpoanie, Horehronie, Zempln, Trenn or Goral in the programme.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="line-height: 1.5;"><strong>Slovak folklore music</strong> induces avery enjoyable atmosphere on any social occasion, therefore we can also meet Your demands in this sphere. Our band together with our female singing group will make Your time pleasant with its repertory as it offers up to several hours of entertainment which arich programme of songs and melodies from around Slovakia and surrounding countries.</span><strong>\n</strong></p><!--:--><!--:de--><p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Ponkame </strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Bohat repertor folklrneho sboru Technik poskytuje znan variabilitu v monostiach.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://localhost/technik/fotovideo/foto/img_2237"><img class="alignleft wp-image-298 size-medium" src="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_2237-300x300.jpg" alt="IMG_2237" width="300" height="300" /></a>Vieme Vm ponknu <strong>komornej program</strong> vtrvan cca 20 mint, ktor je zaujmav najm pre spoloensk podujatia, akmi s recepcie, narodeninov oslavy, rzne firemn udalosti, plesy, posedenia sVaimi obchodnmi partnermi, iprezentcia Vaej spolonosti partnerom vzahrani.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_2417.jpg"><img class=" size-medium wp-image-309 alignright" src="http://localhost/technik/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/IMG_2417-300x200.jpg" alt="IMG_2417" width="300" height="200" /></a>Vprpade zujmu <strong>oceloveern program</strong> Vm vieme ponknu a 100 mint hodnotne umelecky spracovanch piesn atancov zcelho Slovenska vpodan 46 inkujcich. Vprograme njdete reginy Tekova, itnho ostrova, Novohradu, Podpoa